milestones.description: Ganguly and Rahul Dravid's 318-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 236 between Ganguly and Rahul Dravid
Ganguly's 183 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for IND), surpassing Kapil Dev's 175
Ganguly has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (110) in an innings in ODIs for IND, going past Kapil Dev's 100
India's 158-run win against Sri Lanka is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 118-run win against Australia
Ganguly and Rahul Dravid's 318-run partnership is the highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 263 between Aamer Sohail and Inzamam-ul-Haq
Ganguly and Rahul Dravid's 318-run partnership is IND's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 275 between Ajay Jadeja and Azharuddin
